The '''Treitamma Political Center''' was on [[Anchoron]]. The Assistant Director of the center was [[Graskt]].

==History==
The center was to be the site of [[Garm Bel Iblis/Legends|Garm Bel Iblis]]' first major speech against the [[New Order/Legends|New Order]] and the growing powers of [[Emperor/Legends|Emperor]] [[Palpatine/Legends|Palpatine]].
In an effort to assassinate Bel Iblis, a co-founder of the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]], agents of [[Armand Isard/Legends|Armand Isard]] planted a [[Thermal detonator/Legends|thermal detonator]] in the center. Bel Iblis missed the [[Bombing of the Treitamma Political Center|detonation]], but the blast killed his wife [[Arrianya Bel Iblis|Arrianya]] and their two children, as well as Graskt. The explosion destroyed the convention center.

